<item>
            <title>[LU-8705] fix lnet-selftest to be not skipped on DNE</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8705</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4181&quot; title=&quot;lnet-selftest test_smoke: lst error found&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4181&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4181&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; disabled lnet_selftest.sh for DNE:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;commit 9db076aabb2b337b742ae0f91ed6bbe047c67058
Author:     wang di &amp;lt;di.wang@intel.com&amp;gt;
AuthorDate: Thu Oct 31 00:01:15 2013 -0700
Commit:     Vitaly Fertman &amp;lt;vitaly.fertman@seagate.com&amp;gt;
CommitDate: Mon Sep 15 17:59:14 2014 +0400
    LU-4181 tests: disable lnet_selftest.sh &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; DNE.
    Disable lnet_selftest &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; DNE to make review pass with DNE.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4181&quot; title=&quot;lnet-selftest test_smoke: lst error found&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4181&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4181&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; describes different lnet-selftest failures and does not state that the reason of these failures is DNE config.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need lnet-selftest run on Neo based clusters.&lt;br/&gt;
It is reasonable to remove the &quot;skip&quot; added by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4181&quot; title=&quot;lnet-selftest test_smoke: lst error found&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4181&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4181&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
